reviewText: Excellent short version of the tv series about the wildlife off the Californian coast.

Captures the excitement and drama of a spectacle unique on Earth: The once per year congregation of marine life off the coast of Monterey Bay, California. I believe the appearance of the legendary Great Blue Whale is a perfect climax to this event that most of us, sadly, will never witness in person. Here, at least, is the vicarious experience.
